Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:06.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我的名字是古屋萤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.25,0:01:07.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,今天开始上高中一年级
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:11.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我有个引以为豪的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:17.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一个作为班委团结着班级的很厉害的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:20.48,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,虽然因为太过认真找不到女朋友很可怜就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.85,0:01:23.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.69,0:01:25.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,古屋君 又在同一个班呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:28.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,皆川同学 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.82,0:01:29.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:31.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,萤?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.16,0:01:33.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你妹妹?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.66,0:01:34.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:37.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我哥哥承蒙你关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:39.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这么客气 多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.50,0:01:41.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 只是客套话而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:44.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥 这人谁 只是同学么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:47.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,关系好么 还有其他女性朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:49.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喂 萤 很没礼貌诶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.09,0:01:50.97,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你很喜欢你哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:53.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哈? 你在说啥? 这很正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:55.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 这家伙是兄控
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:57.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是挺好的吗 挺可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:02:00.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以你是我哥的什么人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.23,0:02:02.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什么人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.31,0:02:05.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什么人啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:08.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,莫非难道说 你们两个在交往中?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:11.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是 我们只是普通朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.53,0:02:13.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这样啊 我早就觉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.91,0:02:14.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,暂时哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:17.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,萤 痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:19.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,之前我表白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:23.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是没有得到回应 所以说是暂时啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:26.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这家伙在耍你玩 怎么回应早就想好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:28.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嘛 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:33.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎么了? 快点拒绝她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:35.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,让她怀有希望很可怜的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.39,0:02:36.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,萤… 萤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:39.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就是吖古屋君 要拒绝的话就快点吖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:46.69,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 不 我 并 并不是对皆川同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:50.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,拒绝她 拒绝她 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:52.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}也 也不是不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:55.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥你个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:58.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我在担心你啊为什么就不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:01.62,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哥哥你在被玩弄 就算交往也只会受伤而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:05.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,萤 并不是说要交往哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:07.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我这是被拒绝了么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:09.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:11.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,女朋友什么的不需要吧 因为有我就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:13.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 皆川
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:15.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是我没法轻松说出交往吧这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:17.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因为交往之后那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.93,0:03:20.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,结婚什么的 没有经济能力的话孩子也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.89,0:03:24.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我们的事情你已经考虑到这种地步了么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:26.48,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,并不是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:28.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,当然不是这样的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:29.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,只是因为我哥人比较认真
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:32.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是啊 真的很认真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:33.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以才喜欢吖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:38.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那我再试着等一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:40.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:43.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,小萤 能先帮我看着么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不可以 我不会把哥哥让给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:49.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,没关系的哟 我会一起疼爱你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:51.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真是讨厌!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:56.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我没什么特别喜欢的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.51,0:03:59.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,能热衷的兴趣和爱好也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:01.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我自己都觉得自己是无聊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:05.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是大家真的有那么多喜欢的东西么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:07.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:11.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你看起来喜欢星星呢 要不要加天文部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:14.82,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 并没有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.53,0:04:18.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嘛 嘛 只是聊聊天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:19.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你名字是?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:20.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,加贺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:22.78,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,决定了要加什么社团了么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:23.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.87,0:04:27.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那要不要来看看星之管弦乐呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:30.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊嘞 玩笑过头啦!? 啊嘞嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.13,0:04:33.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看星星很开心么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:35.30,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那是当然啊 这么好看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.38,0:04:37.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是只是看的话不会厌倦么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:41.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,会厌倦的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:44.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,没有别的特点什么的了么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:46.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,有! 简单地说就是天文部很受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:49.64,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,现在脱单率高达100%!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:51.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎么样 是不是很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:52.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,说谎的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:55.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,前辈你并不是那么喜欢星星的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:57.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那为什么要在天文部?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:05:02.11,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这个嘛 你看 我喜欢天文部的氛围
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:04.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,诶 还有些什么人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:09.33,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,难道说没了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.66,0:05:12.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,拜托了! 反正你没有其他想加的社团吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:13.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:16.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那我说一个让你对星星感兴趣的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:18.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:22.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那块区域有一个叫做角宿一的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:24.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看起来是一个非常大的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:29.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但其实是两颗相互环绕吸引的星星哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:33.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,两颗星星共同努力的话就可以发出如此耀眼的光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:35.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是不是有点哲学味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:35.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:36.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,有兴趣了么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.40,0:05:38.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,并没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:41.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(1400,200)\fn方正喵呜_GBK\bord1.2\c&H00050606}明明完全抄的学长的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:39.78,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:41.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,没有其他的了么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:43.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(1000,0)\fn方正喵呜_GBK\bord1.2\c&H00050606}明明感觉受教了很多的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:46.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 火星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:50.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看火星时吃的章鱼烧 真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:55.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,已经毕业了的前辈说什么火星人应该就像章鱼一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:58.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以就一边看火星一边烤章鱼烧
Comment: 0,0:05:56.38,0:06:01.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fn方正喵呜_GBK\bord1.2\c&H00050606}然后一边看火星一边烤章鱼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:06:00.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是前辈一直在看火星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:03.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以我一个人大口大口地吃完了
Comment: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:08.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}但是前辈一直在看火星 所以我一个人大口大口地吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:08.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}然后前辈就超级生气 本来他平时脸就好可怕了啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:10.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}其他的比如还有秋天赏月呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.02,0:06:14.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,对这个人而言 天文部是真的非常喜欢的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:15.69,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}夏天一边热火超天地讲着外星人的恐怖故事一遍吃棒冰什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:05.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,已经跟星星没有关系了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:18.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我也能像这样热衷于什么的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.94,0:06:22.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,加贺也来嘛 肯定很会有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.66,0:06:28.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我没有什么特别喜欢的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.62,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一边觉得这样的自己很无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:34.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一边寻找着自己喜欢的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这就是我在寻找的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:38.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是很懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:44.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,总而言之我 想要多看看这份笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.06,0:06:49.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:55.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,邻座的上根同学 总是回避着我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:06:57.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:03.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:08.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,上根还不回家么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:09.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,马 马上就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:12.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也不愿和我对上眼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:14.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我做了什么不好的事情么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:19.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,还是赶紧回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:21.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,刚 刚田君!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:22.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎 怎么了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.51,0:07:23.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.05,0:07:24.63,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,现在 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:26.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我的隐形眼镜掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:28.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:29.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:31.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我出去的时候会注意不踩到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:32.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:33.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,想要你陪我一起找啦!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.23,0:07:36.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,明白了 一起找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:38.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,其实我没被讨厌么…？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.40,0:07:41.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你经常掉隐形眼镜么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:42.69,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,有时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:45.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,比如想要擦擦汗的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:47.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这汗确实不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:49.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,上根
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:52.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,其实你有话想对我说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:59.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我已经做好准备 尽全力回应上根的感情了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:01.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以想说什么就说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.09,0:08:05.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,既然你都说到这种份上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:07.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,应该已经知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.76,0:08:13.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,现在暂时 还没什么头绪就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:15.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,找我到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:17.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,之前上课的时候呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.27,0:08:19.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我因为眼睛不好正在苦恼的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:21.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你把笔记借给我过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.19,0:08:24.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯? 那件事怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:27.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因为 好温柔啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:29.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我是多管闲事了么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:32.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,没有注意到真是抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:34.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,才没有! 不用道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.79,0:08:35.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,找隐形眼镜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:38.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,至少请让我帮你找到…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:45.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,刚田君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:47.01,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯? 找到了么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:48.59,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,答复呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:51.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,答复?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:53.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 也没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:55.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我的感情 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:59.10,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也只是想传达给你而已… 呐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:02.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你这意思是 想看到我的诚意么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:03.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不至于
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:05.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,只是 想知道刚田的想法是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:06.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:07.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:08.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,如果这样能得到你的原谅的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:15.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.58,0:09:19.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我其实 一直都理解不了女生的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:22.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不不 没那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:25.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,如果再接近你的话 肯定会给你添更多麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:34.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这么没用的我 以后还是承蒙照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:39.31,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哼～ 隐形眼镜找到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:41.69,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你怎么哭了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:46.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,刚才你是 能和我交往的意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:47.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,交往?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:50.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,承蒙照顾的话 肯定是要交往的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:54.11,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,谢谢——！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:56.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,没事吧 上根??
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.37,0:09:58.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我说的话很奇怪么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.04,0:10:03.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不不 我这边才是抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:08.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我还没 好好的告白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:08.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an7}注释：告白在日语本意是说出实话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.84,0:10:12.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎么了? 有什么话想说就说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:16.64,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:28.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,未报的雨 落下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:31.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,高野 没带伞么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:35.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,同班的菅原君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:37.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,几乎没和他说过什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:38.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,借给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:41.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我 跑回去就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:42.75,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因为感觉很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:49.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,中途还是一起回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:53.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉呢 和女生一起回家的话会很难堪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:56.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也 也没有 和高野一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:57.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:11:02.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,嗯? 和我这种人传不出什么绯闻的意思么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:03.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:06.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,肩膀淋湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.48,0:11:08.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.86,0:11:10.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那再靠近点?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:15.20,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 再近点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:19.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,高野 不会不好意思么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:20.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,和男生 这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:23.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,反正 也没人在看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:26.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是 要是被喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:27.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看到了之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:31.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,反正 我也没这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:34.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你怎么笑了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:37.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,恋爱这种事情我不是太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:39.14,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那你要是被表白了…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.43,0:11:40.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这种人不存在的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:43.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,只是假设啦 假设你被表白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:46.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,大概会拒绝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:49.48,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,为 为啥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:53.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,因为 对我这种人表白 他肯定不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.94,0:11:56.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我又不可爱 又阴沉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:58.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,才 才没有这种事!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:12:00.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,高野你帮别人做卫生什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:03.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,每天照顾班里的青鳉鱼之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:04.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我都是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:07.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以我 对高野…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:12.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我要在这里坐公交了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,刚才 你对我说了什么么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:21.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 不 什么都…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:24.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,这样 那拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.06,0:12:28.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}恋爱么… 对我来说太勉强了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:32.27,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}菅原君这么温柔 肯定很受欢迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:33.69,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}阿勒?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:38.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}怎么了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:41.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}刚才 要对你说的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:43.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}果然还是决定要说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:47.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}我 我对高野…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:51.13,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}喜 喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:54.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:58.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你是在 鼓励我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:12:58.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}诶!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.51,0:13:00.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不是么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.97,0:13:03.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}是这样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:09.35,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}那 我在这里下车了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:10.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}诶? 拜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:17.94,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}菅原君这人 真是好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}作为借伞的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:22.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}给他做点曲奇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:28.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,下集 至近距离恋爱
Comment: 0,0:00:55.12,0:00:57.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,-------------------OP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:17.87,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}些細な出来事さえも特別だって思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:24.63,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ほらね今も君のこと考えちゃうの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:32.47,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}好きと嫌い交互に数えてゆく占い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:36.31,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}2分の (1の) 確率 (それじゃ)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:40.40,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}踏み出せないね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:48.70,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}きっと Ah この関係はアイマイモコって言うのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:54.16,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}徒然でも I wish I feel my sweet
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:58.25,children opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}大事にしなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:17.87,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}微不足道的事情也会觉得很特别
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:24.63,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}此时此刻也在想念着你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:32.47,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}喜欢与讨厌相互交替的占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:36.31,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}一半一半的概率的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:40.40,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}还是跨不出这一步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.23,0:00:48.70,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我们的关系可以说是暧昧模糊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:54.16,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}虽然无聊但还是希望能感受到属于我的甜蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:58.25,children opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}要珍视这份感情
Comment: 0,0:00:55.12,0:00:57.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,-------------------ED-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.15,0:12:32.90,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}薄れてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:36.07,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}君の面影を
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:40.57,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}見失うのが  怖くて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:43.41,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}たった一瞬の
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:45.87,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}その景色を
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:52.25,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}閉じ込めたくて  だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:57.67,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}あなたに出会えたことで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:13:04.22,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}強くいられたんだ ずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:09.39,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}明日も目が覚めたとき
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:15.27,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}すぐ隣にいる  と思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:21.36,children edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}ただそれだけでいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.15,0:12:32.90,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}逐渐淡薄了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:36.07,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}你的面庞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:40.57,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}害怕这逐渐的  忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.78,0:12:43.41,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}只是一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:45.87,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}想把这份风景
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:52.25,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}锁进我的心里  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:57.67,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}想与你相见这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:13:04.22,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}却很需要勇气  一直如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:09.39,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}明明只是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:15.27,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}明天当我  睁开眼的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:21.36,children edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur5}你能在我身旁而已
